videos.description: Kyle Guy gives the Cavaliers a quick 5-0 lead with a midrange jumper, and then a catch-and-shoot triple on the next possession.
videos.headline: Guy scores first 5 points of game

videos.description: Ty Jerome drops one off to Jack Salt, who powers up and finishes through contact for the bucket and a foul.
videos.headline: Salt uses glass for and-1 finish
